@startuml

class diagram UserSystemRequirement

UserSystemRequirement has class Users, class Requirements, class Relationships

Users is a class with attributes: name, email, phone

Requirements is a class with attributes: id, title, description, date

Relationships is a class with attributes: user_id, requirement_id

UserSystemRequirement has relation Users to Users via identifier "user"
UserSystemRequirement has relation Requirements to Requirements via identifier "requirement"
UserSystemRequirement has relation Relationships to Relationships via identifier "relationship"

@enduml
